---
import Layout from '../layouts/layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Data Policy">
  <section class="prose lg:prose-xl mx-auto py-12 px-4">
    <h1>Spatchat.org Data Policy</h1>
    <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> 05/2025</p>

    <h2>1. Data Collection & Use</h2>
    <h3>User-Uploaded Data</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>GeoTIFFs, CSVs, or other spatial data uploaded for analysis are:</li>
      <ul>
        <li>Processed ephemerally (deleted after 7 days unless retained by user request).</li>
        <li>Never used for training AI models without explicit opt-in.</li>
      </ul>
    </ul>
    <h3>Cookies/Analytics</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>We use anonymized Google Analytics to improve UX (no personal identifiers).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. Data Sharing & Ownership</h2>
    <h3>User Control</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>By default, your data is private and never shared.</li>
      <li>Opt-in to contribute anonymized datasets to:</li>
      <ul>
        <li>Public benchmarking (hosted on Dryad).</li>
        <li>Open-source model improvement (via Hugging Face).</li>
      </ul>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Code & AI Models</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>All code:</strong> <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank">GitHub</a> (MIT License).</li>
      <li><strong>AI models:</strong> <a href="https://huggingface.co" target="_blank">Hugging Face</a> (Apache 2.0).</li>
      <li><strong>Permanent Archives:</strong> Major releases archived via Zenodo (DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.XXXX).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Security</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Encryption: Data in transit (HTTPS) and at rest (AES-256).</li>
      <li><strong>No Sensitive Data:</strong> Do not upload PII (e.g., field coordinates of endangered species).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Compliance</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Aligns with NSF data management requirements.</li>
      <li>FAIR principles (Findable, Accessible, Interoperable, Reusable).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>6. Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:spatchat.org@gmail.com">spatchat.org@gmail.com</a>.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
